modName: High Elf Skin Texture for CBBE
summary: This is a texture replacer that makes the CBBE body skin tones more compatible with the Altmer heads.  Only compatible with CBBE 2 at this time.
descriptionHtml:
All the female bodies in this game (including the vanilla one) are for white girls! :) I got annoyed looking at that, and the horrible neck seam it creates, on my pure mage.  Turned out pretty nice for my 1st mod attempt so I thought I\'d share.  Keep in mind this is a WIP.

*This has not been updated for CBBE 3.0 yet!

Credit:
This is an alteration of \"Calientes Female Body Mod Big Bottom Edition -CBBE-\" texture
http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=2666

This was created using \"Calientes Texture Blender\"
http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=5737

So... much thanks to Caliente and her excellent mods and even more, her tools!

Installation:
Unzip.  Drop the \"textures\" folder into your installation \"data\" folder.

Future Plans:
Replace the hand textures as well.

Get a better color match.

NMM support.  Having a little trouble finding a good walkthrough for this right now.
author: M0rningLightM0untain
